  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study hypothesis is: Pregabalin is superior to placebo in preventing relapse to drinking
      and reducing drinking severity
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a two cell double blind placebo controlled randomized clinical trial of pregabalin
      for alcohol dependence
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
